name: r-rje
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.11.0" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-rje
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/rje_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/rje/rje_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 271504714e6141012d52346116961709e5737774916d1caa423c8e32aa378ddb

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 0
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}              # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_c') }}        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}filesystem        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}make
    - {{ posix }}sed               # [win]
    - {{ posix }}coreutils         # [win]
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-knitr
  run:
    - r-base
    - {{ native }}gcc-libs         # [win]
    - r-knitr

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('rje')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('rje')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=rje
  license: GPL-2.0-or-later
  summary: A series of functions in some way considered useful to the author.  These include functions for subsetting tables and generating indices for arrays, conditioning and intervening in probability distributions, generating combinations and more...
  license_family: GPL2
  license_file:
    - {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
